snippet.title: How Amber Karobkina runs a successful practice featuring Bowen Therapy
snippet.description:
Bowen College Founder Dr. Manon Bolliger, ND chats with Amber Karobkina about how to suggest Bowen Therapy as an option to your clients, how to find clients when you're first starting out, how to use Facebook to grow your business and more! Watch now to listen to this informative chat between two Bowen enthusiasts.  

LIKE OUR VIDEO? Don't forget to subscribe to the Bowen College YouTube Channel.
